text: Literal way I found it was to CTRL-F for Abilities in the ToC to find the section number. Then search for that section number, including the trailing space, to get to that section of the rules. From there, I searched for the word: name and manually scanned from there.
Chrome highlights all instances of a search pattern, so it's quick to do the manual scan from there.
